HIV pixel clustering and cell clustering, 1 pixel clustering dataset (10 passes), 5 replicates of cell clustering (KNN, Leiden, resolution=0.5)

Candace Liu

January 16, 2022

  • First do pixel clustering, then do cell clustering using frequency of pixel clusters
  • Gaussian blur sigma=2, k=20 (pixel metaclusters)
  • For each pixel, divide each marker by total (each pixel sums to 1)
  • Leiden clustering for cell clustering
